" /> <br><sup>'''a c'''</sup> 2<U+2013>4 [[chloroplast membranes]]<ref name="Springer<U+2014>The Chloroplast<U+2014>Chloroplast shapes" /> <!-- <br><sup>'''d'''</sup> 3 [[chloroplast membranes]]<ref name="Springer<U+2014>The Chloroplast<U+2014>Chloroplast shapes" /></span>-->

